title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E101 - Thar Amphala
description: It's time to get turned for Talks Machina! Brian Wayne Foster is joined by Taliesin Jaffe, Ashley Johnson, and Liam O'Brien to discuss episode 101 of Critical Role, give out fan art prizes, and answer questions!
